# Re-include reference data the runtime reads (controls_importer.py looks
# up docs/reference/fair-cam-controls-library.csv for the "Load FAIR-CAM
# library" feature on /controls/import). Without these negations the file
# is stripped from the Docker image and the route reports the file as
# missing.
!docs/reference
!docs/reference/fair-cam-controls-library.csv
